data.description: Price Reduced !!! This 3 bed, 2 bathroom home is situated on a huge lot in a cul de sac.  Featuring an open floor plan and spacious kitchen, this home boasts completely remodeled bathrooms including fixtures, soaking tub in master bath with cultured marble surround, newer roof and paint outside and exterior lighting fixtures. Enjoy year round comfort with furnace and efficient heat pump, 2 car oversized garage with potential for RV parking and a large yard. Huge indoor utility room! Walking distance to schools and shopping this home is perfect for those wanting quiet and space to roam.
